    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"**40 Books Donation List**\"\n#subtitle: \"Bridge Course Level 1\"\nimage: book-donation.png\n#author: \"SARA Institute of Data Science, Sonipat\"\n#date: \"July 3, 2026\" \ndate-modified: last-modified\nformat:\n  html:\n    theme: cosmo\n    toc: true\n    toc-title: \"Contents\"\n    toc-depth: 2\n    toc-location: left\n    code-fold: true\n    code-summary: \"Show code\"\n    self-contained: true\n    page-layout: full\n    css: styles.css\nexecute:\n  echo: false\n  warning: false\n  message: false\n---\n\n\n## About This List\n\n::: {.callout-note icon=false}\n### 📚 How to Donate a Book to SARA\n\nSARA Institute of Data Science is building a **Bridge Course: Level 1** for first-generation learners and students from marginalised communities. You can support us by donating a book from this list in two ways:\n\n- **Send your old copy** - Post your pre-loved book directly to us at the address below\n- **Buy & ship new** - Purchase a new copy online and have it delivered to SARA\n\n**📬 Delivery address:**\nSARA Institute,\nDr. Ambedkar Bhawan,\nKakroi Road, Sonipat\nHaryana - 131001,\nMobile No. +91 925 315 2024\n\n**✉️ Notify us after sending:** [sara.institute.info@gmail.com](mailto:sara.institute.info@gmail.com)\n\n*Please email us with your name and the book title so we can acknowledge your donation and update this list.*\n:::\n\n---\n\n![](book-donation.png){width=\"70%\"}\n\n## Book Donation Tracker\n\nUse the **search box** to find a specific book, or **filter by subject or status** using the column filters below.\n\n::: {.callout-tip icon=false}\n### 🟢 Status Guide\n- 🟢 **Received** - We have this book. Thank you to our donors!\n- 🟡 **In Transit** - A donor has sent this and it is on its way\n- 🔴 **Needed** - This book still needs a donor\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n### Library Progress\n\n::: {.grid}\n\n::: {.g-col-3}\n::: {.callout-note icon=false}\n**📦 Total Books**\n\n# 40\non the wishlist\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.g-col-3}\n::: {.callout-tip icon=false}\n**🟢 Received**\n\n# 2\nalready on the shelf\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.g-col-3}\n::: {.callout-warning icon=false}\n**🟡 In Transit**\n\n# 0\non the way to us\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.g-col-3}\n::: {.callout-important icon=false}\n**🔴 Still Needed**\n\n# 38\nwaiting for a donor\n:::\n:::\n\n:::\n\n**5% of our library goal reached.** Every book brings us closer.\n\n---\n\n### Full Book List\n\n::: {#cell-interactive-table .cell execution_count=4}\n\n::: {#interactive-table .cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<!--| quarto-html-table-processing: none -->\n<table id=\"itables_294dc25b_d1b4_41fe_9782_27ab0a571f39\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"vertical-align:middle; text-align:left\"><a href=https://mwouts.github.io/itables/><svg class=\"main-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"\nwidth=\"64\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 400\" style=\"font-family: 'Droid Sans', sans-serif;\">\n    <g style=\"fill:#d9d7fc\">\n        <path d=\"M100,400H500V357H100Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M100,300H400V257H100Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M0,200H400V157H0Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M100,100H500V57H100Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M100,350H500V307H100Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M100,250H400V207H100Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M0,150H400V107H0Z\" />\n        <path d=\"M100,50H500V7H100Z\" />\n    </g>\n    <g style=\"fill:#1a1366;stroke:#1a1366;\">\n   <rect x=\"100\" y=\"7\" width=\"400\" height=\"43\">\n    <animate\n      attributeName=\"width\"\n      values=\"0;400;0\"\n      dur=\"5s\"\n      repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n      <animate\n      attributeName=\"x\"\n      values=\"100;100;500\"\n      dur=\"5s\"\n      repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n  </rect>\n        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"107\" width=\"400\" height=\"43\">\n    <animate\n      attributeName=\"width\"\n      values=\"0;400;0\"\n      dur=\"3.5s\"\n      repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n    <animate\n      attributeName=\"x\"\n      values=\"0;0;400\"\n      dur=\"3.5s\"\n     